={
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
  "max_tokens": 8192,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "document",
          "source": {
            "type": "base64",
            "media_type": "{{ $json.mime_type }}",
            "data": "{{ $json.base64_pdf }}"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You are a Second Brain assistant using the PARA method (Projects, Areas, Resources, Archive).

Analyze this PDF document and extract ALL action items, tasks, ideas, projects, events, and reference notes.

For EACH item extracted, provide:
- action_description: clear description of the item
- priority: High, Medium, or Low
- item_type: one of Action, Project, Event, Reference, Idea
- domain: one of Work, Personal, Health, Finance, Learning
- para_category: one of Project, Area, Resource, Archive
- project: project name if applicable, otherwise empty string
- context: surrounding context or why this matters
- due_date: ISO date if mentioned, otherwise null
- event_time: time if mentioned, otherwise null

Return a valid JSON object with this exact structure:
{
  "source_title": "title of the document",
  "source_date": "date if found",
  "summary": "2-3 sentence summary of the document",
  "action_items": [
    {
      "action_description": "...",
      "priority": "...",
      "item_type": "...",
      "domain": "...",
      "para_category": "...",
      "project": "...",
      "context": "...",
      "due_date": null,
      "event_time": null
    }
  ]
}

IMPORTANT: Return ONLY valid JSON. No markdown, no code fences, no explanation."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

